                    "_comment": "Particle relaxation time in the Stokes drag regime (particle_relaxation_time, src line 269): τ = ρ_p*d_p^2/(18*μ_air)",
                    "lhs": "τ",
                    "rhs": {
                        "op": "/",
                        "args": [
