                    "_comment": "Brownian diffusion term of the collection efficiency (Eq. 20.53, first line; slinn_collection_efficiency, src line 331): E_diff = (4/(Re*Sc))*(1 + 0.4*sqrt(Re)*Sc^(1/3) + 0.16*sqrt(Re)*sqrt(Sc)). The upstream cbrt(Sc) is re-expressed as Sc^(1/3) (no cbrt op in spec §4.2); Sc > 0 always, so the two are equivalent.",
